casebody.data:
No. 09-34. Pfizer Inc., Petitioner v. Rabi Abdullahi, et al. 561 U.S. 1041, 130 S. Ct. 3541,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1121,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5541. June 29, 2010.

Motion of Washington Legal Foundation, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice and Justice So-tomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.

Same case below, 562 F.3d 163.
